  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 3rd level, your confidence propels you into battle. You can give yourself a bonus to your initiative rolls equal to your <strong>Charisma modifier</strong>.</p>\n<p>You also gain an additional way to use your @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.ZNG4a61hajMEzhb1]{Sneak Attack}; you don't need <strong>advantage </strong>on the attack roll to use your Sneak Attack against a creature if you:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>are within 5 feet of it,</li>\n<li>no other creatures are within 5 feet of you,</li>\n<li>and you don't have <strong>disadvantage </strong>on the attack roll.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All the other rules for Sneak Attack still apply to you.</p>",
